      "description": "Honest used car in poor condition, best suited for a buyer looking for a budget vehicle, project, or something to fix up. It has significant wear and visible cosmetic blemishes, and buyers should expect mechanical needs, deferred maintenance, and a rougher overall driving experience than a well-kept daily driver. This is not a clean or turnkey example, but it could make sense for someone comfortable putting in work.",
