    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This is an honest fair-condition car that should appeal to someone looking for a usable driver rather than a showpiece. It presents decently overall, but it does show noticeable age, wear, and cosmetic imperfections consistent with a vehicle that has been used and not fully restored. Expect a serviceable interior and exterior with flaws you\u2019ll see up close, along with the kind of general wear that comes with an older, average-condition example. It should make a reasonable project to improve over time or simply enjoy as-is if you want an affordable entry point, but buyers should not expect mint or fully sorted condition.",
