    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Priced to sell, this is a fair-condition car that still has good everyday value for someone shopping on a budget. It presents decently overall and has clearly been used, with cosmetic and age-related wear that\u2019s consistent with its condition, but it remains a straightforward, affordable option. If you want a usable car at a sensible price and don\u2019t need a perfect example, this one is worth a look.",
